Template-Plugin-Lingua-EN-Inflexion v0.01
-----------------------------------------

Released 13th January 2020.


DESCRIPTION
-----------

This plugin may be used with Template Toolkit to provide an interface
for Lingua::EN::Inflexion in your templates.


INSTALLATION
------------

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION
-------------------------

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Template::Plugin::Lingua::EN::Inflexion

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        https://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Template-Plugin-Lingua-EN-Inflexion
	
	MetaCPAN
		https://metacpan.org/pod/Template::Plugin::Lingua::EN::Inflexion


